_sText: Gg_stone_town v1.0 ---------------------- Although more of a fy map this little town brings you the fast paced action you crave for a great gun game experience. Take your fight above or underground and chose from the many paths which may take you behind enemy lines. SMG'S and Shotguns are the most deadly weapons for this map. -32 Spawn Points (although 24 is more than enough) -HDR -Buy Zones Enjoy.
